    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Faiths that occurred in the early years of Buddhism, in South and Southeast Asia. In Hindu-Buddhism, ideas and dieties of the two faiths were combined, as Buddhism first grew out of Hinduism in India in the 6th century BCE. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
